OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThis evening
OL,6,Fwill be dry with some late sunshine.
OL,7,FThen the rest of the night will be dry
OL,8,Fwith variable amounts of cloud. Light
OL,9,Fwinds.
OL,10,
OL,11,CFriday:FApart from one or two light
OL,12,Fshowers it will be dry with a few
OL,13,Fbright or sunny spells.
OL,14,
OL,15,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:
OL,16,FOutbreaks of rain will spread east on
OL,17,FSaturday, occasionally heavy later.
OL,18,FScattered showers on Sunday. Further
OL,19,Frain likely on Monday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
